As promised, I've partially dampened my activities.
For example, my deputy will be the travel agent in the spring.
People would like me to be the Samaritan who would save the Republic.
But I need to make a living, too.
How much did you usually make as a businessman?
200 to 400 grand, which I'm taking.
And if I were president, I'd shut down my business.
